text: Heini Lautala (born August 28, 1977 in Vehkalahti in present Hamina) is a Finnish rhythmic gymnast. Lautala competed for Finland in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. There she was 23rd in the qualification round and did not advance to the final. == References == == External links == * Heini Lautala at Sports- Reference.com Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:People from Hamina
